headline: Procter And Gamble Rejoins USA Gymnastics With Long Term Olympic Bet
summary: Procter & Gamble (NYSE:PG) has renewed its top-level sponsorship of USA Gymnastics. The partnership runs through the 2028 Los Angeles Olympics. The deal marks P&G's return as a primary sponsor after previously ending the relationship following a high-profile scandal. For a consumer products group like Procter & Gamble, which owns brands across household, personal care and health categories, high-visibility sports platforms can be an important way to keep products front of mind with...
